window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Jessika first met billionaire Asher Landseer, CEO of Landseer Enterprises, she never anticipated becoming wrapped up in a scheme of corporate deception and cutthroat business practice. She also never expected romance or to fall in love, especially with Asher himself. But, everything that's happened, is it real? She has no time for doubts, no chance to second guess her decisions; at least not now. </p> <p>With Beatrice Landseer and Solomon Royce's plans revealed, the only thing left for Jessika and Asher to do is stop them. Except, how? And what if it's too late? Solomon has one conclusive trick up his sleeve that even Beatrice didn't know about and he plans to succeed at destroying Asher's life no matter the cost. What will happen once the billionaire's final ultimatum is issued? </p> <p><b>NOTE:</b> This sizzling contemporary BDSM erotic romance audiobook contains themes of domination and submission. </p>"; 
